---
title: Logo
description: Informations about your brand
page_title: Logo
page_emphasis: Guide about your brand
layout: components
---

.row
  .medium-12.columns
    .row
      .medium-10.medium-centered.columns
        h2 Brand assets
        h3 #{data.settings.site.title} logo
    .row
      .medium-8.columns
        = image_tag 'logos/foundation-boilerplate.png', alt: 'foudnation-boilerplate logo guidelines'
      .medium-4.columns
        p
          'The #{data.settings.site.title} marks include, but are not limited to, the #{data.settings.site.title} name, the #{data.settings.site.title} logo, phrase, image or other designation that identifies the source or origin of any of #{data.settings.site.title}’s products.
        = link_to "#{data.settings.site.source_code}/archive/gh-pages.zip", class: 'button' do
          i.fi-download
          'Download the assets

    .layout-section
      .row
        .medium-10.medium-centered.columns
          h3 Favicons
      .row
        .medium-12.columns
          ul.small-block-grid-2.medium-block-grid-6
            li = image_tag "#{data.settings.site.url}favicon-196x196.png"
            li = image_tag "#{data.settings.site.url}favicon-160x160.png"
            li = image_tag "#{data.settings.site.url}favicon-96x96.png"
            li = image_tag "#{data.settings.site.url}favicon-32x32.png"
            li = image_tag "#{data.settings.site.url}favicon-16x16.png"

    .layout-section
      .row
        .medium-10.medium-centered.columns
          h3 Usage guidelines
          p The #{data.settings.site.title} marks represent the core values of our brand …
      .row
        .medium-6.columns
          = image_tag 'logos/dont.png'
        .medium-6.columns
          markdown:
            __Don’t:__

            - Rotate or change the direction of the logo
            - Animate the logo
            - Change the color of the logo
            - Add special effects to the logo
            - Use older versions of the logo, previous logos, or any marks that may be confused with the brand
